Define a button to click: you can define a button. Auto means you have to
define 4 images for the button and it will use them automaticly:
buttonname_idle.png, buttonname_.hover.png,
buttonname_selected_hover.png, buttonname_selected_idle.png.
Then after the auto statement "button_name_ % s "
Then define the action what will happen after you use the button.
#imagebutton auto "button_%s.png":
    #action [Function(incrementTotal), SelectedIf(total % 2 ==1)]
